SubjectMUSKOWEKWAN BAND - Setting apart.
PrecisSetting apart of 60.124 hectares (148.57 acres) of surface lands including mines and minerals, situated in the Rural Municipality of Kellross No. 247, near the Village of Lestock, Saskatchewan, as Muskowekwan Indian Reserve No. 85-57.
